Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Two adjoining lots sold in one line

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and Knight Frank are pleased to present the opportunity to purchase a large size freestanding site in a core Western Sydney precinct. 

The building benefits from the below features;

+ Total site area: 10,694 sqm* rectangular site
+ Two adjoining lots sold in one line
+ Two level high quality office/warehouse on 61-63 Mandarin Street– suitable for corporate headquarters
+ IN1 General Industrial and IN2 Light Industrial for flexible zoning
+ Gantry cranes 
+ 1 + 1 year lease back
+ Three street frontages in one of Western Sydney’s premier locations
+ DA lodged for 49 industrial units with concept plans
+ Opportunity to occupy, invest or redevelop

FOR SALE BY PUBLIC AUCTION; 
DATE: WEDNESDAY 5TH  JUNE 2019, 2:00PM 
LOCATION: CBRE OFFICES - GROUND FLOOR, 10-14 SMITH STREET, PARRAMATTA

*approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: PROMINENT INDUSTRIAL SITE IN ESTABLISHED WESTERN SYDNEY LOCATION - 10,694SQM*

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and Knight Frank are pleased to present the opportunity to purchase a medium size freestanding facility in a core Western Sydney precinct. 

The building benefits from the below features;

+ Freestanding building – 1,200 sqm*
+ Site Area – 1,391 sqm*
+ Zoned IN1 General Industrial for multiple industrial uses
+ Internal clearance of up to 8 metres 
+ Access via container height roller door
+ 1+1 year lease back
+ 2 x Gantry crane

FOR SALE BY PUBLIC AUCTION; 
DATE: WEDNESDAY 5 JUNE 2019, 2:00PM  
LOCATION: CBRE OFFICES - GROUND FLOOR, 10-14 SMITH STREET, PARRAMATTA

*Approximate

The property is located on the northern side of Lisbon Street approximately 450m west of Woodville Road. 

A prominent industrial location occupied by a variety of users of both a local and regional nature. Access to the M4 and the M5 Motorways is via Woodville Road and Henry Lawson Drive.

- 2,187sqm* building area
- Dangerous goods approved
- Internal clearance of up to 12.3m*
- Accessible via two (2) container height roller doors
- Large awning for all weather loading 
- Excellent truck access through a large hard stand forecourt
- Corporate office component fully carpeted & air conditioned.
- Fully sprinklered facility 
- Zoned IN1 General Industrial 

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact either of the exclusive agents listed.

*approx.

CBRE is pleased to present 34-38 Lisbon Street, Fairfield East to the market for sale. The opportunity exists for a savvy investor or owner occupier to make use of the high building area and unlock its strong yield potential through multiple income streams.

34-38 Lisbon Street, Fairfield East boasts the following key attributes:

- Building area of 6,359sqm*
- Site area of 7,174sqm*
- 667sqm* basement storage or parking
- Internal warehouse clearances of up to 13m*
- Features an office/showroom, warehouse facility and freestanding office building
- Refurbished office and showroom currently utilised for kitchens and bathrooms
- Opportunity for vendor to leaseback part of the premises on a 5 year lease*
- Strong yield potential via multiple income streams
- Vacant possession also available
- Lounge suites, karaoke rooms and open room areas 
- Two substations on site 

For a copy of the information memorandum or to arrange an inspection, please contact the either of the listed agents.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present 17 Lisbon Street, Fairfield East to the market for sale via Public Auction. Set on over 5,500sqm, the site offers an array of options to developers, investors & owner-occupiers alike.

17 Lisbon Street, Fairfield East boasts the following key attributes:
- Underdeveloped site ready for expansion
- Situated in the heart of the Fairfield East industrial precinct & in close proximity to Woodville Road 200m*, The Horsley Drive 1.9km* & The Hume Highway 2.5km*
- Site area of 5,574sqm*
- Building area of 1070sqm*
- Fully secured site with an electronic security gate
- First floor office with own amenities including kitchenette
- Warehouse is accessed via one (1) container sized roller shutter door
- Potential for future development (STCA)
- Twelve (12) month leaseback to the vendor

The Public Auction will be held onsite on Tuesday, 22nd October2019 at 2:00pm.

To discuss the property in further detail, please contact the exclusively listed agents.

*approx.
